OL,3,CFive people arrested after #500k worth
OL,4,Cof plant machinery stolen
OL,6,FFive people have been arrested after
OL,7,Fhalf a million pounds worth of plant
OL,8,Fmachinery was stolen in Hampshire.
OL,10,FOfficers conducted warrants and
OL,11,Fsearches in Southampton and Totton on
OL,12,FWednesday.
OL,14,FThey seized a number of items,
OL,15,Fincluding some suspected counterfeit
OL,16,Fcigarettes and a forklift.
OL,18,FA man in his 50s and four others - all
OL,19,Fin their 40s - were arrested on
OL,20,Fsuspicion of conspiracy to commit
OL,21,Fburglary.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
