OL,3,CFive people arrested after #500k worth
OL,4,Cof plant machinery stolen
OL,6,FThe arrests form part of an ongoing
OL,7,Finvestigation into the alleged theft
OL,8,Fof plant machinery, RHIBs, generators
OL,9,Fand fuel from across Southampton and
OL,10,Fthe surrounding areas.
OL,12,FIt's estimated that around half a
OL,13,Fmillion pounds worth of equipment has
OL,14,Fbeen stolen in more than 30 incidents
OL,15,Fbetween February 5, 2025 and April 17
OL,16,Fthis year.
OL,18,FThe force is urging people to keep
OL,19,Freporting crimes and suspicious
OL,20,Fincidents in rural areas or on
OL,21,Fbuilding sites.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
